# Dependency lockfiles + npm manifest — intentionally untracked.
# This fixture exists only as a parsing target for the LSP integration
# tests; its transitive deps never ship and never run as an app. Tracking
# the lockfiles surfaced 50+ Dependabot alerts for vulnerabilities that
# pose no real risk. CI regenerates vendor/ via `composer update`.
# composer.json stays tracked (PSR-4 + package-priority routing tests).
/composer.lock
/package.json
/package-lock.json
